        "package_button_background": "#e6b325",
        "package_button_text_color": "#ffffff",
        "package_button_hover_background": "#e6b325",
        "image_border_radius": 8,
        "show_collapsible_1": true,
        "collapsible_1_title": "7-Day Appointment Guarantee",
        "collapsible_1_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_1_content": "<p>At Laser Skin Clinics, we guarantee that all customers can be seen within 7 days of their enquiry.</p>",
        "show_collapsible_2": true,
        "collapsible_2_title": "C02 Price match guarantee",
        "collapsible_2_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_2_content": "<p>C02 is our go-to treatment for so many skin concerns because we believe it delivers unmatched, transformative results. We want every client to experience the brilliance of C02, which is why we offer a <strong>Price Match Guarantee</strong> on both <strong>single sessions and multi-session bookings</strong>.</p><p>If you find a <strong>like-for-like C02 treatment</strong> at a cheaper price anywhere in Wolverhampton, we’ll <strong>match that price</strong>  and give you a <strong>£50 voucher</strong> to spend at Laser Skin Clinics.</p><p>Premium results, guaranteed value.</p>",
        "show_collapsible_3": false,
        "collapsible_3_title": "Booking Process",
        "collapsible_3_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_3_content": "<p>Once you’ve completed your online booking, a member of our team will contact you via phone, WhatsApp, or email to schedule your appointment.</p>",
        "show_collapsible_4": true,
        "collapsible_4_title": "Securing your booking",
        "collapsible_4_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_4_content": "<p>A small deposit of £30 will be required to secure your booking. Should you wish to go ahead we will take the £30 off the total price of your treatment cost. </p>",
        "show_collapsible_5": true,
        "collapsible_5_title": "Payment Options & Finance",
        "collapsible_5_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M7 8h10M7 12h4m1 8l-4-4H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-3l-4 4z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_5_content": "<p>Treatments can be paid for by cash or card on the day of your appointment. We also offer Klarna Finance and Shopify instalment options for added flexibility. If you’d like to pay using one of these methods, just let us know and we’ll guide you through it.</p>",
        "show_collapsible_6": true,
        "collapsible_6_title": "Contact and address",
        "collapsible_6_icon": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z\"></path></svg>",
        "collapsible_6_content": "<p>If you have any questions or would like help with your booking, our team is here to assist. Simply click speak to a specialist or our direct details are below.</p><p><strong>Phone:</strong> 01902 256667</p><p><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 07798 983387</p><p><strong>Email:</strong> info@laserskinclinics.co.uk</p><p><strong>Clinic Address:</strong></p><p>Laser Skin Clinics<br/><br/>4 Perton Farm Barns<br/><br/>Jenny Walkers Lane<br/><br/>Wolverhampton<br/><br/>WV6 7HB</p>",
        "show_faq_link": true,
        "faq_pre_text": "Have more questions?",
        "faq_link_text": "View FAQs",
        "faq_section_id": "shopify-section-template--25630357193084__ss_simple_faq_jiYFWj",
        "faq_link_url": ""
      }
