      "name": "Info Hero",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "What is the MelanoPro System?",
        "body": "<p>The Melanopro Peel System is a professional depigmentation treatment developed to target stubborn, resistant pigmentation concerns such as melasma, sun damage and post-inflammatory discolouration.</p><p>Unlike superficial chemical peels that focus only on exfoliating the surface of the skin, Melanopro is designed to address pigment activity at a deeper level. It works by combining controlled resurfacing with melanin-regulating ingredients to help visibly reduce uneven tone and support clearer skin over time.</p><p><strong>This is a structured protocol, not a one-step facial.</strong></p>",
        "points_heading": "",
        "footer_text": "<i>The goal is controlled, progressive correction rather than aggressive stripping of the skin.</i>",
        "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/image_6ea584d3-29b6-4fd2-b1b1-724a00ef63a4.png",
        "bg_position": "right center",
        "section_height": 600,
        "overlay_strong": "#ddd2c8ed",
