      "name": "How It Works Timeline",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Understanding the MelanoPro Peel Process & Skin Timeline",
        "description": "<p>The <strong>MelanoPro Peel System</strong> is a professional depigmentation treatment designed to target stubborn pigmentation such as melasma, sun damage and post-inflammatory discolouration.</p><p>The peel is applied in clinic and left on the skin for a prescribed number of hours before being washed off at home. Over the following days, the skin enters a controlled peeling phase as pigmented cells are shed.</p><p>This structured process helps improve overall skin clarity and promote a more even skin tone.</p>",
