      "name": "Info Hero",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "What Results Can You Expect?",
        "body": "<p>The MelanoPro Depigmentation Peel System is designed to gradually reduce visible pigmentation and restore a clearer, more even complexion.</p><p>Rather than simply exfoliating the surface of the skin, the MelanoPro protocol works to regulate pigment activity while accelerating the removal of pigmented skin cells. This structured process helps improve overall skin clarity and reduce the appearance of stubborn pigmentation concerns.</p><p>Most clients begin to notice visible improvements in skin tone and brightness once the peeling phase has completed and fresh skin has emerged.</p>",
        "points_heading": "",
        "footer_text": "<i>Results develop progressively as the skin completes its renewal cycle. For deeper or long-standing pigmentation concerns, a series of treatments or a structured pigment management plan may be recommended to achieve optimal results.<i></i></i>",
