      "settings": {
        "heading": "How CO2 Works & What to Expect",
        "description": "<p><strong>CO2</strong> uses controlled pulses of laser energy to target pigment within the hair follicle. The energy heats and disables the follicle at the root, reducing its ability to regrow hair without damaging the surrounding skin.</p><p>Hair grows in cycles, which is why a course of treatments is required for best results.</p>",
